cs.CL, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.CV 

This paper deals with natural language understanding for robotics, which falls under the intersection of several CS sub-fields. The most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language) as the paper focuses on natural language processing and understanding. The second most likely category is cs.RO (Robotics) as the paper deals with the application of natural language understanding in robotics. The third likely category is cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as the paper involves machine learning and agent training. The fourth likely category is cs.LG (Learning) as the paper discusses the use of clarification dialogs to improve language parsing and concept grounding. The fifth likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision) as the paper involves the perception of physical objects in the environment.
